# .distignore — paths that must NOT ship to a production Joist install.
#
# @purpose Single source of truth for what is excluded when assembling the
#          deployable plugin dist. Consumed by deploy-plugin.sh via
#          `rsync --exclude-from` (rsync mode) and as a filter list when
#          staging the dist before an lftp/sftp mirror.
#
# Format: one rsync-style pattern per line. Leading/trailing whitespace and
# blank lines are ignored; lines starting with '#' are comments. Patterns are
# matched relative to the plugin root (the dir containing joist.php).
#
# WHAT SHIPS (for reference — do NOT add these here):
#   joist.php, uninstall.php, README.md, joist.constitution.md
#   src/            (PSR-4 PHP — EXCEPT src/admin-app, see below)
#   assets/         (front-end JS/CSS incl. assets/widget-pack/motion runtime)
#   build/          (compiled wp-scripts bundle — this is what AssetEnqueue reads)
#   languages/      (if present)
#
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Dev dependencies & build inputs (never ship)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
node_modules/
package.json
package-lock.json
.npmrc

# React admin-app SOURCE. The COMPILED output lives in build/ and DOES ship.
# Only the un-compiled source tree is excluded here.
src/admin-app/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Tests & fixtures (never ship)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
tests/
phpunit.xml
phpunit.xml.dist
.phpunit.result.cache

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Source maps & build noise (never ship — leaks source, bloats payload)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.map
*.log
.cache/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# VCS, tooling, CI, repo scaffolding (never ship)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.git/
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.github/
.distignore
scripts/
.tenet/
.editorconfig
.eslintrc*
.prettierrc*
.stylelintrc*
composer.json
composer.lock

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Editor / OS noise (never ship)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
Thumbs.db

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# In-repo developer docs that are not end-user plugin docs.
# README.md DOES ship; the skills/ knowledge tree does not.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
skills/
LESSONS.md
